OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FLondon mayor Sadiq Khan thanked his
OL,7,F"friend and colleague for over three
OL,8,Fdecades" after Sir Keir Starmer said
OL,9,Fhe would resign as Prime Minister and
OL,10,Fleader of the Labour Party.
OL,12,FSir Keir asked Labour's governing body
OL,13,Fto set out a timetable to replace him,
OL,14,Fbeginning on July 9, and ending by the
OL,15,Fsummer recess to "ensure a new leader
OL,16,Fis in place before Parliament returns
OL,17,Fin September".
OL,19,FLondon's mayor said Mr Starmer was a
OL,20,Fman of "great integrity" who devoted
OL,21,Fmuch of his career to public service.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G1/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
