PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,F"Keir Starmer has made a huge
OL,7,Fcontribution to the Labour party and
OL,8,Four country, and I want to thank him.
OL,9,FHe is only the fifth Labour leader to
OL,10,Fhave won a general election, which has
OL,11,Fallowed him to deliver real progress,"
OL,12,FSir Sadiq said.
OL,14,F"This includes bringing national rail
OL,15,Fservices into public ownership,
OL,16,Fgetting NHS waiting times down,
OL,17,Frolling out free breakfast clubs and
OL,18,Fstrengthening the rights of workers
OL,19,Fand renters.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G2/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BLondon NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,380,370,120,260,000,100
PN,37903
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,F"These are meaningful changes that
OL,7,Fwill improve the lives of people in
OL,8,FLondon and right across Britain for
OL,9,Fyears to come," he added.
OL,11,FLondon's mayor also had a message for
OL,12,Fwhoever takes over in Downing Street
OL,13,Fand said the party had a "huge
OL,14,Fmandate" and and people were
OL,15,F"impatient for change".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G3/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
