OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FHe also said London should not miss
OL,7,Fout on investing, adding: "The local
OL,8,Felection results showed that people
OL,9,Fare impatient for the change that was
OL,10,Fpromised and a Labour government that
OL,11,Fholds firm to the progressive values
OL,12,Four party was established to promote.
OL,14,F"This should be the focus of the next
OL,15,FPrime Minister.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G4/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
