OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,F"It's also crucial that the new Labour
OL,7,Fleader invests in every part of the
OL,8,Fcountry. This includes London, which
OL,9,Fis central to delivering for the rest
OL,10,Fof the country. We must use the
OL,11,Fpotential of our capital to boost the
OL,12,Fnational economy and raise living
OL,13,Fstandards - for the benefit of
OL,14,FLondoners and people right across the
OL,15,Fcountry."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G5/10
