OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FSir Keir Starmer was visibly upset as
OL,7,Fhe said he planned to spend time being
OL,8,Fthe "best husband" and "best dad I can
OL,9,Fto my beautiful children", after he
OL,10,Fannounced his resignation as Prime
OL,11,FMinister.
OL,13,FThe Prime Minister's voice wavered as
OL,14,Fhe concluded the speech setting out an
OL,15,Fend point for his time inside No 10
OL,16,FDowning Street, which follows months
OL,17,Fof pressure for him to stand down and
OL,18,Fmake way for a new Labour leader.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G6/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
