PN,37907
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FSir Keir's voice broke as he said:
OL,7,F"When I leave the biggest job in the
OL,8,Fcountry, I shall spend more time on
OL,9,Fthe most important job: being the best
OL,10,Fhusband I can to my fantastic wife,
OL,11,FVic, who has been a rock by my side
OL,12,Fthrough good times and bad, and being
OL,13,Fthe best dad I can to my beautiful
OL,14,Fchildren, who are my pride and my joy."
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G7/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
