CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FA growing number of Labour MPs were
OL,7,Flosing confidence in Sir Keir's
OL,8,Fability to lead the country after a
OL,9,Fseries of what were widely viewed as
OL,10,Fpolicy mistakes, and because they did
OL,11,Fnot believe he could meet the
OL,12,Fchallenge from Nigel Farage's Reform
OL,13,FUK at the next election.
OL,15,FLabour former minister Andy Burnham,
OL,16,Fwho returns to Parliament on Monday
OL,17,Fafter winning the crucial Makerfield
OL,18,Fby-election, and ex-health secretary
OL,19,FWes Streeting, have both said they
OL,20,Fwill stand in a contest to succeed Sir
OL,21,FKeir, should one be held.
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G8/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
