PN,37909
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F379A1782224342
OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FFormer health secretary Wes Streeting,
OL,7,Fwho had been viewed as Andy Burnham's
OL,8,Fmain rival for the Labour leadership,
OL,9,Fsaid he would back the new Makerfield
OL,10,FMP for the job.
OL,12,FHe said he had "spoken at length with
OL,13,FAndy in recent days".
OL,15,FMr Streeting said he was convinced
OL,16,Fthat Mr Burnham "is committed to
OL,17,Fbuilding an inclusive party that draws
OL,18,Fon the best of our political
OL,19,Ftraditions and that he can win the
OL,20,Ffight of our lives against the force
OL,21,Fof nationalism".
OL,1,W h7}h7}j7}h7}h7}                 G9/10
OL,2,W+,"-'*%/*-'"-'*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
