OL,3,CStarmer resigns: Mayor thanks friend
OL,4,Cand urges next PM to invest in London
OL,6,FCalling for a coronation for Mr
OL,7,FBurnham, he said: "We could spend the
OL,8,Fsummer exaggerating small differences,
OL,9,For we can roll up our sleeves and help
OL,10,Fhim to deliver the change our party
OL,11,Fand our country needs.
OL,13,F"That is the choice that I am making
OL,14,Fand I hope that everyone else will
OL,15,Fback Andy too."
